cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

This paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically the task of removing rain effects from images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a deep learning-based approach, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves modeling and refining the results, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
